== 经济 ==

钢铁产量的减少也减少了宾夕法尼亚州的煤矿开采，这对约翰斯敦的经济很重要。1982年，约翰斯敦任职时间最长的市长小赫伯特·普富尔(Herbert Pfuhl Jr.) 表示，由于衰退，城市收入下降了大约35%。<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/1982/10/03/us/steel-industry-woes-weigh-heavily-on-johnstown.html " October 3, 1982. Retrieved July 24, 2019.]</ref>

约翰斯敦的经济后来有所恢复，主要是由于医疗保健和高科技国防工业，<ref>[https://www.towncharts.com/Pennsylvania/Economy/Johnstown-city-PA-Economy-data.html "Johnstown, Pennsylvania Economy Data", ''Town Charts'', Retrieved July 24, 2019.]</ref>但据报道，它是 2017 年美国萎缩速度第三快的城市，2011-2017年间，横跨坎布里亚县的约翰斯敦都会区失去了 5.5% 的人口。<ref>[https://whyy.org/articles/johnstown-area-third-fastest-shrinking-city-in-the-us/ "Johnstown area third fastest shrinking city in the U.S." by Eleanor Klibanoff, ''WPSU'', April 11, 2017. Retrieved July 24, 2019.]</ref>尽管如此，在 2018 年，约翰斯敦还是被福布斯评为美国“最佳商业和职业小场所”第 169 位。<ref>[https://www.forbes.com/places/pa/johnstown/ "The Best Small Places For Business And Careers", ''Forbes'', 2018. Retrieved July 24, 2019.]</ref>

